column5: YEah!  I read this article today....very interesting read!
That is one COOL fish lol

So what you think? A bad boy tipped with minnow? or a spreader? lol .....It's great that there are still new species being found but at the expense of our ice shelfs ??? it's a bit scary to me. Has anyone seen the movie by Al Gore called an inconvienent truth? great movie but a little scary. Really cool fish though.
